file.name: swagger.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Swagger for dnscollector tool
  version: 0.13.0
  description: This is a swagger for the API of the dnscollector.
  contact:
    email: d.machard@gmail.com
  license:
    name: MIT
    url: 'https://github.com/dmachard/go-dnscollector/blob/main/LICENSE'
  x-logo:
    url: ''
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:8080/'
paths:
  /metrics:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Metrics in prometheus format
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Get metrics
  /reset:
    delete:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Reset metrics
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Reset metrics
  /top/requester:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Top source ip requesters
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Top source ip requesters
  /top/requester/suspicious:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Top suspicious requesters ip list
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Top suspicious requesters ip list  
  /top/tld:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Top first level domains list
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Top first level domains list
  /top/fqdn:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Top domains list
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Top domains list
  /top/fqdn/nxd:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Top NX domains list
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Top NX domains list
  /top/fqdn/slow:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Top Slow domains list
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Top Slow domains list
  /top/fqdn/suspicious:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Top suspicious domains list
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Top suspicious domains list         
  /top/as:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Top Autonomous System list
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Top Autonomous System list
  /dump/requester:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Return full list of requesters
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Return full list of requesters 
  /dump/fqdn:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Return full list of domains
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Return full list of domains
  /dump/tld:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Return full list of top level domains
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Return full list of top level domains
  /dump/as:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: stream
          schema:
            type: string
          description: stream name
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Return full list of Autonomous System
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
      summary: Return full list of Autonomous System
security: []
externalDocs:
  url: 'https://github.com/dmachard/go-dnscollector'

Error: notImplemented: path "/dump/fqdn": get: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
